# disallow-metrics

If we deny intentions and/or set a cluster's [`acl.default_policy`](https://developer.hashicorp.com/consul/docs/agent/config/config-files#acl_default_policy) to "deny", what metrics do we get from a downstream proxy trying to call an upstream one?

Docs:

- https://github.com/hashicorp-education/learn-consul-hashiconf-2023/tree/main
- https://developer.hashicorp.com/consul/docs/agent/config/config-files#acl_default_policy
